Most Haunted S11E12 Fort Delaware

Location(s): Fort Delaware, Pea Patch Island, Delaware

On this episode of Most Haunted, the Most Haunted Team Heads to Delaware to investigate Fort Delaware, which was once used to house over thirty thousand prisoners during the war. Originally built to protect the ports of Philadelphia and Wilmington from invasion then home to some 13000 prisoners, Fort Delaware is a huge imposing location.With so many different places over such a large area, the team had their work cut out to investigate the Fort before sunrise.
